AC Gilchrist 154: highest ODI score by an Australian (prev. DM Jones 145 v England at Brisbane, World Series Cup, 1990/91 and RT Ponting 145 v Zimbabwe at Delhi, Pepsi Triangular Cup, 1997/98)

milestones.description: Gilchrist has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (80) in an innings in ODIs for AUS, going past Ricky Ponting's 78
Gilchrist's 154 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for AUS), surpassing Dean Jones's 145
